### BoardBuddies Game Session API Collection
### 게임 세션 관련 API 요청들

### Create a game session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "boardGameId": 1,
  "hostUserId": 1,
  "maxPlayers": 4,
  "scheduledDate": "2024-01-15T19:00:00",
  "location": "강남구 카페",
  "description": "보드게임 같이 해요!"
}

### Get game session by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions/1

### Get all game sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions

### Join game session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions/1/join
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 2
}

### Leave game session
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions/1/participants/2

### Update game session
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxPlayers": 6,
  "scheduledDate": "2024-01-15T20:00:00",
  "location": "홍대 보드게임카페",
  "description": "시간 변경! 보드게임 같이 해요!"
}

### Search game sessions by location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game-sessions/search?location=강남구
